In the English countryside, 
Luke Edward Hall's Cotswolds home has a view of the Mediterranean. Inspired and joyful, the artist's house represents his universe in its cheery abundance. 
Come along on a guided tour. @lukeedwardhall 
#diptyqueparis #summeressentials #mediterranean #summer

The film "A Scent in a Song" tells the story of how Olivier Pescheux and Lewis OfMan created the music of our new eau de parfum. Between scent and syncopation, Orphéon plays until dawn. 

#diptyqueparis #unleashimagination @lewisofman  @olivierpescheuxparfumeur 
#song #music #jazz #bossanova #perfume

node.title: The curtain rises on Orphéon in song.

Graphic design
has always been a part of diptyque. For our 60th anniversary, we asked the designer, artistic director and professor Yorgo Tloupas to take us back to the origins of the graphic arts. We're pleased to share this story with you. 
#diptyqueparis #diptyque #graphics #yorgotloupas @yorgotloupas
